description:
Select the ship to fire and choose a location above the red line 
to create an explosion and stop the enemy laser.
Shoot the ufo when possible.
&lt;span class="redactor-invisible-space"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="redactor-invisible-space"&gt;There is a time between one shot and another, but if you 
select another ship that time is over.
&lt;span class="redactor-invisible-space"&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;If dont fit, try change to fullscreen mode.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
